Former Senate Leader, Victor Ndoma-Egba, has lost his wife, Amaka, in a motor accident along the Benin-Akure Road. Details of the accident was not very clear at the time of this report. Victor Ndoma-Egba Ndoma-Egba had earlier in the year lost his mother in-law while his house was reportedly burgled during the violence perpetrated by thugs during the nationwide protest against police brutality in the country.